  "gwSpecs": {
    "description": "Built on the success of the original SPYRA, SPYRA II increases output and creative effect capabilities while maintaining an extremely compact form factor with infinite pan/tilt. Incorporating a 200W, 8,000K cold-white LED engine, SPYRA II delivers piercing output with a sharp 2-degree, hotspot-free beam. Its refined optics optimize throw distance and features 3 dynamic overlapping prisms including a 45deg, 48-facet prism for exciting mid-air looks. SPYRA II offers fast pan/tilt movements with 360-degree infinite rotation capabilities, complemented by 13 intense colors including (2) CTO filters + CTB filter, frost filter, and 15 static gobos. All combined into a lightweight design with remarkable power efficiency.",
